#

Classic Veggie Burger

25 min
$5.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

egg

Dietary Tags:

vegetariangluten-free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

easyhealthyquick

Description

A delicious, hearty veggie burger packed with flavor and nutrients, perfect for a quick meal!

Ingredients

  • black beans: 1 can, drained and rinsed
  • oats: 1 cup
  • carrot: 1, grated
  • bell pepper: 1, finely chopped
  • onion: 1, finely chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • egg: 1
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
  • cumin: 1/2 teaspoon
  • burger buns: 2
  • lettuce: 2 leaves
  • tomato: 1, sliced
  • avocado: 1/2, sliced
